Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A silver bell rolled from the clouds\Nand landed beside a tiny red panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The red panda spotted a lost duckling\Nfollowing the bell's soft sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A puddle blocked the little duckling\Nfrom reaching its waiting family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The clever red panda placed broad leaves\Nacross the water like stepping stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The duckling crossed safely, then the\Nsilver bell jingled with happy golden light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone waved as the bell floated back toward\Nthe same cloud where the adventure began.
